  "keyFeatures": [
    "Zero world generation by default — full developer control over game world",
    "Multi-threaded tick system using ThreadDispatcher and TickThread",
    "Hierarchical event system with filterable EventNode trees",
    "Command framework with type-safe arguments and tab-completion",
    "Dynamic registries for dimensions, biomes, enchantments, and more",
    "NIO-based networking with packet-level access",
    "Acquirable API for safe cross-thread entity access",
    "Adventure library integration for rich text and audio",
    "Built-in pathfinding with AI goal/target selectors",
    "Anvil world format support and procedural chunk generation API"
  ],
